Stamp   966222558
To      immortal~
Subject New labels~
Text
There are now two labels added to stat:
load and clone

What this means generally is that if you load an item, it'll flag
the item 'Loaded by: imm_name'.

This also applies for cloning an item, by adding 'Cloned by: imm_name'.

This way, we can track anything loaded and/or cloned and it's not a
flag so it's not able to be modified by set or any other means.

Also, two minor spelling errors have been fixed. One for stopping pkquests
and the other for 'Admin don't have access to passwords.' on the intro.

Usagi's room added, complete with a botch on my part which will be fixed
upon next reboot.

--Vorlin
~
