Subject NEW STUFF!~
Text
After a long and overdue wait, we've got a TON of changes that deserve
mentioning. Of course, some idiot declared more than allowed ranks in the
clan information and that's why we failed to reboot for so long.

`&1``: Feed - revamped, complete with day/night damage difference.
`&2``: Optic blast - revamped
`&2``: Throw - revamped
`&3``: Kamehameha wave - revamped
`&4``: Slayer spells - revamped, if you have them, you should like them more
`&5:`` Scribe/brew - spell/object levels are now more even, more for espers
`&6``: Possess - revamped completely, more evened out
`&7``: Hurricane kick - revamped
`&8``: Dragon punch - revamped
`&9``: Added '`^rsay``, `^dtoggle``, and new prompt info (see helps for these)
`&10``: Added '`^who np``' to show non-pkers
`&11``: Counter will not work against backstab attacks or anything that
`     you're not immediately fighting (multiple players/mobs/etc)

`!Revamped`` means that lag is random for successful hits or fails, damage
is more evened out (if it was fubared), and overall well-balanced.

These changes have been in effect for at least 5 days and tested by
multiple players on port 9010 (my test port I have running with my
changes specifically). Comments/complaints are most welcome but remember
that we're really working on things here to better this place and it's a
`%LOT`` more productive for you to complain in a CIVIL tone and with a
reason, not just because you think your player now sucks because it's
evened out. 
Thanks go out to the entire ACTIVE imm staff as well as the entire 'pbase'
on port 9010 that have provided me with ideas and suggestions.
Without these people, I definitely wouldn't have attempted this.

--Vorlin/Todd, one imm who really DOES try, just ask his gf...
~
