Stamp   1019328427
To      all~
Subject PK_Rules~
Text
Ignorance to these rules will NOT be an excuse. So read up.
Duels:
When you agree to a duel you make the word of duel law.
Meaning if you get a buddy to jump in or you see a duel
going on and you shoose to interfear, your busted.

Clans:
1) You can NOT attack another claned person in their turf.
2) You can invade and attack only when an offical clan war has started
3) Clan wars will last 2 weeks. Most kills at the end of the war gets stuff.
4) If you are in a fight and someone gates to their own turf
`7   you can give chase. You cant flee to avoid death.
5) Only clan members may start a fight in their own area. This goes
`7   for unclanned people as well. You cant attack someone when
`7   you are in a clan area.
6) All fighting taking place outside of clan areas are free for all.
`7   So watch your back when not in a clan area.

So basically use common sence. Make PK a stratagy and war thing. Not a
"He has good eq so I will loot it" thing. Also looting will be changed.
That and more rules to come soon.
~
