Sender  Kevin~
Date    Fri Jul 19 19:49:59 2002~
Stamp   1027126199
To      all~
Subject Group EXP~
Text
Here's how the new system works.

A group of two will get full experience.
Every person beyond the second will reduce the award by 15%, to a minimum of 40%.
3-member group: 85% experience
4-member group: 70% experience
5-member group: 55% experience
6+ member group: 40% experience

This should promote grouping, on a small scale (5 members, tops).
Leaving group xp unchecked is like leaving your house unlocked
in a big city; both are ripe for exploitation.
~
Sender  Kevin~
