Low end cleric spells (save heat metal) have been updated. Give earthquake, dispel good/evil, flamestrike,
and the harmful spells a try.

Healing spells have been made more potent.

Demon ninjas/thieves cannot be made anymore, and gunshot AC damage reduction has been adjusted(downwards).

All of these remain subject to change.
